Maksym Bondarenko, Victor Hugo Fernandez Arraya, Denis Ecknauer
EISTI. Cergy, 2016. 

Every file of this project includes:

- Calibration of financial trees (binomial and trinomial)

- Calculation of option prices depending on time and underlying prices change

- Pricing option at time t = 0 and underlying price known

- Creation of random path

- Surfacing the option price dynamics

- Pricing exotic options s.t. Barrier option, Condor option.

- VaR (level x) calculation for every type of the option

- Pricing options using trinomial trees

